## **Phase 2 — Push (triggers Amplify / ECS)**

```powershell
$env:GH_TOKEN = [Environment]::GetEnvironmentVariable('GH_TOKEN', 'User')
$env:GIT_SSL_NO_VERIFY = 'true'

# Work branch (if different from deploy)
git push origin <work-branch>

# Deploy branch
git push origin <deploy-branch>
```

**Batch example (all six repos):**

```powershell
powershell -NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File `
  "F:\project_workspace\application-deployments\documentation\aws-infrastructure\_private\scripts\Invoke-ReleaseDeployAll.ps1"
```

(Ensure `GH_TOKEN` is set in the parent shell or script loads it from User env.)

